Package: tidyGWAS
Type: Package
Title: Quality control for GWAS summary statistics with minimal filtering
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Arvid Harder
Maintainer: Arvid Harder <arvid.harder@gmail.com>
Description: 
    tidyGWAS employs a version of dbSNP transformed into Apache Arrow parquet
    files to restore and validate genome wide association summary statistics.
